headline: Conagra Brands: Poor Operating Results But Steeply Discounted Valuation
summary: Conagra's Q4 results and '26 guidance disappointed, yet valuation offers optimism. Explore potential growth via asset sales or M&A. Read why I'm continuing my CAG buy rating.
